text: Eacles cuscoensis is a moth in the family Saturniidae. It is found in Peru. & 2009c.Two new species of the genus Eacles Hübner 1819 [1816] (Lepidoptera: Saturniidae). Entomo-satsphingia 2(2): 8-10. ==References== Category:Ceratocampinae Category:Moths described in 2009
